9. The cinema has just heard that they will be holding an exclusive midnight showing of 'Guardians of the Galaxy 2'!!
   Create a new entry in the 'movies' table to reflect this.

  UPDATE movies SET show_time = '00:00' WHERE title = 'Guardians of the Galaxy 2';

   id |                title                | year | show_time
