10. The cinema would also like to make the Guardian movies a back to back feature. Update the 'Guardians of the Galaxy'
    show time from 18:55 to 21:30

    UPDATE movies SET show_time = '21:30' WHERE title = 'Guardians of the Galaxy';
    UPDATE movies SET show_time = '00:00' WHERE title = 'Guardians of the Galaxy 2';

